text: chaur puok anak changcha( nouv nie k meat) nowpel del trong ban bangkeut puok anakchea anak snang( krobkrong phendei) banteabpi ad haey trong ban phtal lomnow dthan aoy puok anak now leu phendei daoy puok anaksaeang sang vimean now leu deirab ning chaoh phnom chea chrei n thveuchea phteah . dau che neah chaur puok anak changcham ubkarkoun teanglay robsa a l laoh haey chaur puok anak kom braprutte batolmeusa now leu phendei aoy saoh
